The camera sweep found two actual fixed-fraction camera smoothers: FreeChase zoom recovery and 
FreeCamera’s scripted interpolation fraction. The FreeCamera one is editor/free-fly camera state 
interpolation, not chase gameplay; I’m now checking whether player/remote creature controllers have 
the same pattern or whether their smoothing uses `elapsedTime`.
