| Highest for door snap mechanics | [FreeChaseCamera.cpp:691](/D:/Code/swg-client-v2/src/engine/client/library/clientGame/src/shared/camera/FreeChaseCamera.cpp:691), [FreeChaseCamera.cpp:739](/D:/Code/swg-client-v2/src/engine/client/library/clientGame/src/shared/camera/FreeChaseCamera.cpp:739) | Instant assignment to collision distance, no smoothing | Not a smoothing constant, but frame-cadence-sensitive. More FPS means more hit/miss samples while crossing a door edge; flicker can happen at higher temporal frequency. |
