| Medium for remote creatures/NPCs | [RemoteCreatureController.cpp:64](/D:/Code/swg-client-v2/src/engine/client/library/clientGame/src/shared/controller/RemoteCreatureController.cpp:64), applied at [RemoteCreatureController.cpp:468](/D:/Code/swg-client-v2/src/engine/client/library/clientGame/src/shared/controller/RemoteCreatureController.cpp:468) | Fixed per-frame speed decay `*= 0.75` | Yes. Stop decay half-life is ~2.4 frames: ~80 ms at 30 FPS, ~20 ms at 120 FPS. Remote creatures snap to stopped animation/motion faster at high FPS. |
